{
  "stem": "3346.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, that there are working places where you can-- where other people work, but they help you to-- there's somewhere a little room where you can stay with the other children.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You manage.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not-- yes, I did what-- I had to go to the Appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no way out of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to be counted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because otherwise there would be somebody missing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were about-- at that time, there were about 60-- between 60 and 90 children in the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I don't remember, really.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember that I, I was sick quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, a friend of my mother's.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Giza Schein.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think my mother was taken to to the [GERMAN] before, and that I was left behind initially in, in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And then, again, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] somehow I got to the [GERMAN] at one time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not initially.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know my parents were there, and then I was with them for not too long a period of time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was about six months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we were at-- my mother and I were sent back to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm not sure whether my father was already then sent to Gross-Rosen, or later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he, he wa-- he wasn't with us in Plaszow afterwards because that was when the big Aussiedlung came, when they closed Plaszow down.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Something did happen before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- you know that-- I assume you know by now that each camp had a Jewish sort of-- they had the German director, et cetera, and then they had Jewish director.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
